{"tid":1539162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實獨立調查委員會都好危險","createTime":"2019-09-04T09:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T09:25:26.000Z","uid":134093,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3a9a4d12870b99e76e867a025bf255720676e493","tid":1539162,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:04:54.000Z","msg":"點組成無人講<br />\n點執行又無人提<br />\n最慘係要查幾耐無人知<br />\n到件事淡左先查到幾件出黎已經無意思<br />\n<br />\n最怕有部分人收左貨，少左示威<br />\n個爭取力又低左<br />\n<br />\n係人都知和理非佔多數，到時候再有示威<br />\n政府都可以標籤佢地做極端分子<br />\n一網打盡，到時莫講話五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n以後有乜都唔會爭取到，港澳辦已經有風聲傳緊<br />\n會推國民教育，但你覺得仲有下次抗爭咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府一直無正面回應係雙真普選<br />\n因為係政府死穴，反對= 欺騙市民<br />\n贊成又無可能。<br />\n連人權法都係要求落實雙普選<br />\n反而你地無人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果一陣真係有林奠記者會，記者真係要問下<br />\n<br />\n點解從來都無回應過落實普選呢個訴求<br />\n呢個除左係示威者訴求，亦都係全港市民既應有權利"},{"pid":"b41d693f12a6e76628d4585d908b17ab2febb4bd","tid":1539162,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fc0351ce272e6bf417cf21c1b005c21f4a941d","tid":1539162,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「文宣」林鄭三次對話前科，拆穿假面具<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1510024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1510024</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「五大訴求；決一不可」</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d685049be3dc65dcebb542cd0cbd902e8b6495a2","tid":1539162,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e692dd95b038779194ff2874369e8120c1ce84a","tid":1539162,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72211e046db4fc8b381afb643abb3cbee1bd12a9","tid":1539162,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf6f9bae910af6e281dbd8883aeadfa61dcf266","tid":1539162,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e720cae3d7d8e8766809b0194489503c589988dc","tid":1539162,"uid":186800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"點解無人諗過獨立調查會再揪多d 前線出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f754b5319f89f04b2f8122844df9a294b329408","tid":1539162,"uid":278712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"係，鉛水事件就是這樣。<br />\n所以這些訴求是「基本」，不是「終點」。"},{"pid":"83eae4802e4447229df6f7c3d34096d2b478d7a2","tid":1539162,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e720cae3d7d8e8766809b0194489503c589988dc","tid":1539162,"uid":186800,"li